{"type": "article", "id": 28420, "title": "流水打造的刀", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-20T06:55:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021627273h8bP10wLfsEMlZu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>水刀（waterjet）制作是一种用高压水流对材料进行快速侵蚀和切割的数控加工方式（CNC），在这个过程中水会渗入材料当中使它失去压力，导致精度下降。通过这种特别的制作工艺，新西兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.markwilsondesign.co.nz/\">Mark Wilson</a> 把 Hardox 钢锻造成了边缘有不规则波纹的刀 Kanagawa（神奈川）。造型的灵感来源于日本浮世绘画家葛飾北斎的名作《神奈川沖浪裏》，通过器械特意制作的缺陷展示了流水的强大力量。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162725LAhdDvtTeFopKmbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162725jGqkNYgcDzbp6ZaF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162726EZQVhR3xi8ykzc7m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216272685ABz3rhwjtkpdoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}